theorem Topology.closure_eq_interior_union_frontier
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    closure A = interior A ∪ frontier A := by
  ext x
  constructor
  · intro hx
    by_cases hInt : x ∈ interior A
    · exact Or.inl hInt
    ·
      have hFront : x ∈ frontier A := And.intro hx hInt
      exact Or.inr hFront
  · intro hx
    cases hx with
    | inl hInt =>
        exact interior_subset hInt
    | inr hFront =>
        exact hFront.1

theorem Topology.innerInterior_subset_interiorClosure {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A : Set X} :
    interior A ⊆ interior (closure A) := by
  intro x hx
  exact (interior_mono (subset_closure : A ⊆ closure A)) hx
